      "markText": "母亲也不愿意，似乎在她看来，一旦在里面种上些什么，便意味着将要永远留在这里。",
      "totalCount": 1350,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1360&rangeEnd=1398",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1360&rangeEnd=1398"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_6_16516-16588",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "16516-16588",
      "markText": "丢下被我打破了膝盖的亚历山德罗，走到他的书包旁，打开包，取出他的球拍放进我的拍套。我没有对他说这不过是一次公平的交换，也不期待他的道歉或是补偿。",
      "totalCount": 896,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16516&rangeEnd=16588",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16516&rangeEnd=16588"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_6_13637-13674",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "13637-13674",
      "markText": "这下他们记起了我是个女人，而他们则同为男人，于是出乎意料地结成了新的同盟。",
      "totalCount": 784,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13637&rangeEnd=13674",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13637&rangeEnd=13674"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_6_16796-16880",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "16796-16880",
      "markText": "在公共花园摘玫瑰，没有按时把书还给图书馆，张着嘴巴等饭吃，在应急车道超车，为了几颗水果糖和孩子们吵架，说谎，使坏。也许这些都不算什么，但实际上，我们就是这样慢慢变坏了。",
      "totalCount": 784,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16796&rangeEnd=16880",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16796&rangeEnd=16880"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_3_3679-3723",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3679-3723",
      "markText": "而我仿佛就在现场，站在房间的角落里，看着母亲的一举一动，我审判着她，我想，我不会原谅她。",
      "totalCount": 759,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3679&rangeEnd=3723",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3679&rangeEnd=3723"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_3_3548-3614",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3548-3614",
      "markText": "他们抬着她，把她举了起来。他们抓住她的胳膊和腿，她的衬衣被扯开，露出没有钢圈的胸罩和隆起的乳房；她的裙子也开裂了，能看见里面的内裤。",
      "totalCount": 675,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3548&rangeEnd=3614",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3548&rangeEnd=3614"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_8_7890-7915",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "7890-7915",
      "markText": "如果你不富有，便只剩一样东西能拯救你，那就是美貌。",
      "totalCount": 672,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=7890&rangeEnd=7915",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=7890&rangeEnd=7915"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_4_1614-1704",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1614-1704",
      "markText": "父母做“那种事”时，床铺吱吱嘎嘎的声音听得一清二楚，毕竟我们的家不过就是一个房间，你既不能待在外面，也无法把自己关进卫生间，因为无论在哪儿，家里的声音总能一点不落地钻进你的耳朵里。",
      "totalCount": 630,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1614&rangeEnd=1704",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1614&rangeEnd=1704"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_6_14070-14107",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "14070-14107",
      "markText": "是我供你们吃穿，离了我，你们什么都不是。母亲猛地把盘子摔在桌上，站了起来。",
      "totalCount": 612,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14070&rangeEnd=14107",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14070&rangeEnd=14107"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_4_14789-14820",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "14789-14820",
      "markText": "只要坚持，直到达成目的，只要你坚持再坚持，就没有什么得不到的。",
      "totalCount": 576,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14789&rangeEnd=14820",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14789&rangeEnd=14820"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_6_16288-16345",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "16288-16345",
      "markText": "我高高举起球拍，双手握住拍柄，朝着他的膝盖打了下去。一下，两下，三下，五下。打到第七下的时候，他哀号着倒在了地上。",
      "totalCount": 550,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16288&rangeEnd=16345",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16288&rangeEnd=16345"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_10_21473-21491",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "21473-21491",
      "markText": "潘多洛蛋糕掉在地上，没有人打开礼物。",
      "totalCount": 540,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=21473&rangeEnd=21491",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=21473&rangeEnd=21491"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_13_1776-1822",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1776-1822",
      "markText": "你没有来我的高中毕业考试，当然这是因为我不让你来，其实我希望你不要听我的话，可是你没有明白。",
      "totalCount": 540,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1776&rangeEnd=1822",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1776&rangeEnd=1822"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_6_3868-3917",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3868-3917",
      "markText": "我点头附和，但嫉妒如同潜行的蛇，见不得光，被我仔细地埋在心底，小心地养在体内，一有机会就喂上一口。",
      "totalCount": 528,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3868&rangeEnd=3917",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3868&rangeEnd=3917"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_8_8057-8122",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "8057-8122",
      "markText": "我不想再做之前那个满是缺点的小女孩，我想成为被人爱慕的女人。这种转变让我心痒难耐，于是我一头扎进了这场关于身体与凝视的病态竞争中。",
      "totalCount": 522,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8057&rangeEnd=8122",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8057&rangeEnd=8122"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_8_8938-8963",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "8938-8963",
      "markText": "对他们，我只感到厌恶，想把他们埋进土里，扬到风中。",
      "totalCount": 518,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8938&rangeEnd=8963",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8938&rangeEnd=8963"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_4_15137-15173",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "15137-15173",
      "markText": "我们不可能成为安东尼娅，我们永远做不到，永远赢不了人生里的任何一场战斗。",
      "totalCount": 516,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=15137&rangeEnd=15173",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=15137&rangeEnd=15173"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_6_12934-12963",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "12934-12963",
      "markText": "父亲担心我羽翼未丰，没有父亲的保护，就要独自面对这个世界。",
      "totalCount": 510,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300141009&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=12934&rangeEnd=12963",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/49032310813ab9d94g019991?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=12934&rangeEnd=12963"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300141009_5_13767-13803",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "13767-13803",
